Question: Join orders and products to retrieve product names and quantities for order ID 1024.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "orders", "columns": ["products.name", "order_items.quantity"], "where": "orders.id = order_items.order_id AND order_items.product_id = products.id AND orders.id = 1024", "limit": 20 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "Wireless Mouse", "quantity": 2}, {"name": "USB-C Cable", "quantity": 5}, {"name": "Laptop Stand", "quantity": 1}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 18 }
