Question: Join users and orders to find the status of the most recent order for user ID 55.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "users", "columns": ["orders.status", "orders.order_date"], "where": "users.id = orders.user_id AND users.id = 55", "limit": 1 }
Response: { "rows": [{"status": "shipped", "order_date": "2023-11-15"}], "count": 1, "query_ms": 9 }
