Question: List supplier names and product titles by joining suppliers and products where the supplier is based in 'Germany'.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "suppliers", "columns": ["suppliers.name", "products.title"], "where": "suppliers.id = products.supplier_id AND suppliers.country = 'Germany'", "limit": 25 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "Berlin Parts GmbH", "title": "Precision Gear"}, {"name": "Munich Electronics", "title": "Logic Board v2"}, {"name": "Hamburg Textiles", "title": "Cotton Fabric Roll"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 15 }
